---
import InvestLayout from '../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import Disclosure from '../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout
  title="Why Now"
  titleVi="Vì sao ngay bây giờ"
  description="Three converging forces make now the right time to invest in Nguyen AI Computer: AI agent adoption, Vietnam privacy law 91/2025, and the Nguyen demographic."
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16" aria-label="Why now overview">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">Why Now</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Vì sao ngay bây giờ</p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-ink-muted max-w-3xl">
      Three converging forces create a unique investment window for Nguyen AI Computer.
      <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">Ba lực lượng hội tụ tạo cửa sổ đầu tư duy nhất.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Force 1: AI agent adoption -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-8 card-hover">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-gold">01</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink">AI Agent Adoption is Accelerating</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Adoption AI Agent đang tăng tốc</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold/40 pl-4">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold">62%</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">
            McKinsey: percentage of organizations using AI agents in at least one business function (2024).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold/40 pl-4">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold">46%</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">
            Microsoft: percentage of employees using AI agents at least weekly in their workflow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-muted">
        The market has moved from experimentation to deployment. Nguyen AI Computer is positioned to ride this wave with a purpose-built Agent team for the Nguyen community.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Force 2: Vietnam privacy law -->
    <div class="mt-8 bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-8 card-hover">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-gold">02</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink">Vietnam Privacy Law 91/2025</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Luật bảo vệ dữ liệu cá nhân Việt Nam 91/2025</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-muted">
        Vietnam's Personal Data Protection Decree (PDPD 91/2025) mandates strict consent, data minimization, and privacy-by-design. This creates regulatory tailwinds for privacy-first platforms like Nguyen AI Computer, where living-person data is private by default, family trees are private by default, and users own their data vault.
        <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">Nghị định 91/2025 yêu cầu đồng ý rõ ràng, tối thiểu hóa dữ liệu, và quyền riêng tư theo thiết kế — tạo lợi thế cho nền tảng riêng tư như Nguyen AI Computer.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Force 3: Nguyen demographic -->
    <div class="mt-8 bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-8 card-hover">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-gold">03</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink">The Nguyen Demographic</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Nhân khẩu học Nguyễn</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold/40 pl-4">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold">31.57%</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">of Vietnam's population shares the Nguyen surname</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold/40 pl-4">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold">~31M</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">people in Vietnam alone, plus a large global diaspora</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-gold/40 pl-4">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gold">2nd</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">most common surname in Vietnam, among the largest globally</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink-muted">
        No incumbent AI or genealogy platform specifically serves this community with bilingual, privacy-first, AI-native tools.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Validation: Ancestry/MyHeritage -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Market Validation</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Xác nhận thị trường</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
          <div class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">$4.7B</div>
          <h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-ink">Ancestry.com (2020)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">Acquired by Blackstone — validates the genealogy and heritage market at scale.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6 card-hover">
          <div class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">$600M</div>
          <h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold text-ink">MyHeritage (2023)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-1">Acquired by Francisco Partners — confirms continued investor appetite for heritage platforms.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
